     specify custom quantities via ‘projoint_qoi’; if provided, its
     ‘structure’ and ‘estimand’ override ‘.structure’ and ‘.estimand’.

     Valid ‘se_type_*’ values depend on clustering:

        • Without clusters: ‘"classical"’, ‘"HC0"’, ‘"HC1"’, ‘"HC2"’,
          ‘"HC3"’

        • With clusters: ‘"CR0"’, ‘"CR1"’, ‘"CR2"’, ‘"stata"’, ‘"none"’

     If ‘NULL’, _estimatr_ defaults are used (‘HC2’ when unclustered;
     ‘CR2’ when clustered).

